        term:orderedNote              ( "A thoroughfare is usually a street, but it might be a waterway or some other feature. For example, \"Avenue des Champs-Élysées\".\n\nThe concept definition is based on the EU Core Location Vocabulary."@en "The concept thoroughfare is just a part of \"streetAddress\" in Schema.org; example:\nstreetAddress: \"38 avenue de l'Opéra\"\nthoroughfare: \"avenue de l'Opéra\""@en );
        term:orderedSynonym           ( <urn:uuid:cdc31107-5f91-4442-beeb-af09460bfc36> ) .

