        skos:note                     "The question whether a natural person actually &quot;owns&quot; or &quot;controls&quot; the agent is decided separately in each national jurisdiction. It is also dependent on the legal form of the agent. <br />Based on Directive (EU) 2015/849 Artcicle 3, section 6"@en;
        skos:prefLabel                <urn:uuid:21c855a5-fc02-43d9-b3f2-4c913109e99f>;
        skos:related                  webuild:concept-41;
        suomi-meta:creator            "5dc030a4-740f-4dde-9548-4e6e797899d8";
        suomi-meta:modifier           "5dc030a4-740f-4dde-9548-4e6e797899d8";
        suomi-meta:publicationStatus  <http://uri.suomi.fi/codelist/interoperabilityplatform/interoperabilityplatform_status/code/DRAFT>;
        term:orderedBroader           ( webuild:concept-6005 );
        term:orderedNote              ( "The question whether a natural person actually &quot;owns&quot; or &quot;controls&quot; the agent is decided separately in each national jurisdiction. It is also dependent on the legal form of the agent. <br />Based on Directive (EU) 2015/849 Artcicle 3, section 6"@en );
        term:orderedRelated           ( webuild:concept-41 ) .

