webuild:concept-100  rdf:type         skos:Concept;
        dcterms:created               "2025-12-04T13:05:46.444Z"^^xsd:dateTime;
        dcterms:modified              "2026-01-23T14:58:21.848Z"^^xsd:dateTime;
        skos:altLabel                 <urn:uuid:38d50945-6756-45eb-966b-e8668571d25d>;
        skos:broader                  webuild:concept-93;
        skos:definition               "a set of data that enables the establishment of the identity of a European Business Wallet owner and that is issued by a provider of European Business Wallet owner identification data"@en;
        skos:inScheme                 webuild:;
        skos:note                     "At minimum, the \"EBWOID\" includes legal name + one or more legal identifiers (e.g., EUID or national identifier), and may include additional matching attributes under policy."@en;
        skos:prefLabel                <urn:uuid:346cac64-695d-436e-a8b4-daba8723e44d>;
        skos:related                  webuild:concept-98 , webuild:concept-7 , webuild:concept-14;
        suomi-meta:creator            "5dc030a4-740f-4dde-9548-4e6e797899d8";
        suomi-meta:modifier           "5dc030a4-740f-4dde-9548-4e6e797899d8";
        suomi-meta:publicationStatus  <http://uri.suomi.fi/codelist/interoperabilityplatform/interoperabilityplatform_status/code/DRAFT>;
        term:orderedBroader           ( webuild:concept-93 );
        term:orderedNote              ( "At minimum, the \"EBWOID\" includes legal name + one or more legal identifiers (e.g., EUID or national identifier), and may include additional matching attributes under policy."@en );
        term:orderedRelated           ( webuild:concept-7 webuild:concept-14 webuild:concept-98 );
        term:orderedSynonym           ( <urn:uuid:38d50945-6756-45eb-966b-e8668571d25d> ) .

webuild:concept-94  rdf:type          skos:Concept;
        dcterms:created               "2025-12-04T12:47:24.424Z"^^xsd:dateTime;
        dcterms:modified              "2026-03-03T06:05:42.321Z"^^xsd:dateTime;
        dcterms:source                "COM(2025) 838 - Proposal for a Regulation on the establishment of European Business Wallets";
        skos:broader                  webuild:concept-41;
        skos:changeNote               "alternative definitions:\n\"a natural person, legal person or group of such persons, including temporary associations of undertakings, when acting in a commercial or professional capacity for purposes related to their trade, business, craft or profession\"\n\"any natural or legal person or public entity or group of such persons and/or entities, including any temporary association of undertakings, which offers the execution of works and/or a work, the supply of products or the provision of services on the market\"";
        skos:definition               "an agent acting in a commercial or professional capacity for purposes related to its trade, business, craft, or profession"@en;
        skos:inScheme                 webuild:;
        skos:note                     "Natural persons can be economic operators; whether they are treated as “legal entities” depends on whether they have a legally recognised registered business identity in the relevant legal context."@en , "“Economic operator” is a capacity/role. \n\nThe same underlying entity may or may not be an economic operator depending on context. \n\nEconomic operators frequently correspond to \"legal entities\" for regulated processes, but the precise coverage depends on the applicable legal instrument."@en , "NB: the exact scope of the \"economic operator\" concept depends on the legal instrument (procurement vs market surveillance vs sector laws)."@en;
        skos:prefLabel                <urn:uuid:a53404ff-d71b-40bc-999e-01588fddb37f> , <urn:uuid:b369f9d8-b167-44bd-a5a5-8c72b4b3363b> , <urn:uuid:0fd08ec7-8001-446d-a3a3-aab584f573bf>;
        skos:related                  webuild:concept-109 , webuild:concept-6006 , webuild:concept-6005;
        suomi-meta:creator            "5dc030a4-740f-4dde-9548-4e6e797899d8";
        suomi-meta:modifier           "5dc030a4-740f-4dde-9548-4e6e797899d8";
        suomi-meta:publicationStatus  <http://uri.suomi.fi/codelist/interoperabilityplatform/interoperabilityplatform_status/code/DRAFT>;
        term:orderedBroader           ( webuild:concept-41 );
        term:orderedNote              ( "“Economic operator” is a capacity/role. \n\nThe same underlying entity may or may not be an economic operator depending on context. \n\nEconomic operators frequently correspond to \"legal entities\" for regulated processes, but the precise coverage depends on the applicable legal instrument."@en "Natural persons can be economic operators; whether they are treated as “legal entities” depends on whether they have a legally recognised registered business identity in the relevant legal context."@en "NB: the exact scope of the \"economic operator\" concept depends on the legal instrument (procurement vs market surveillance vs sector laws)."@en );
        term:orderedRelated           ( webuild:concept-6006 webuild:concept-109 webuild:concept-6005 );
        term:orderedSource            ( "COM(2025) 838 - Proposal for a Regulation on the establishment of European Business Wallets" ) .

webuild:concept-96  rdf:type          skos:Concept;
        dcterms:created               "2025-12-04T12:52:03.06Z"^^xsd:dateTime;
        dcterms:modified              "2025-12-11T15:32:21.384Z"^^xsd:dateTime;
        skos:broader                  webuild:concept-6006;
        skos:definition               "a Union entity, national, state, regional or local authority, a body governed by public law, an association formed by such entities or bodies, or a private entity mandated by at least one of them to provide public services, when acting under such a mandate"@en;
        skos:inScheme                 webuild:;
        skos:narrower                 webuild:concept-97;
        skos:prefLabel                <urn:uuid:f3583d2c-35bd-4821-add3-350e1bbc4121>;
        skos:related                  webuild:concept-98;
        suomi-meta:creator            "5dc030a4-740f-4dde-9548-4e6e797899d8";
        suomi-meta:modifier           "5dc030a4-740f-4dde-9548-4e6e797899d8";
        suomi-meta:publicationStatus  <http://uri.suomi.fi/codelist/interoperabilityplatform/interoperabilityplatform_status/code/DRAFT>;
        term:orderedBroader           ( webuild:concept-6006 );
        term:orderedNarrower          ( webuild:concept-97 );
        term:orderedRelated           ( webuild:concept-98 ) .

webuild:concept-6006  rdf:type        skos:Concept;
        dcterms:created               "2023-11-09T13:34:04Z";
        dcterms:modified              "2026-01-23T14:38:10.967Z"^^xsd:dateTime;
        <http://purl.org/termed/properties/id>
                "42ea77c6-99e7-44fd-91b4-33a2f179018d";
        skos:broader                  webuild:concept-41;
        skos:changeNote               "alternative definitions:\n1. \"a natural person or a legal person that is recognised by a legal system as capable of holding rights and obligations\"\n2. \"a formal organization that is involved in economic activity\"";
        skos:definition               "an agent whose identity is legally recognised for transactions and that can be referenced unambiguously by a legal identifier issued or recognised by a competent authority"@en;
        skos:inScheme                 webuild:;
        skos:narrower                 webuild:concept-98;
        skos:note                     "In WE BUILD, “legal entity” is intended as the transactional/legal identity used in B2B/B2G processes. It can include: a legal person (e.g., company), and in jurisdictions where applicable, a natural person acting as a registered business actor (e.g., sole trader) whose business identity is legally recognised and identifiable."@en , "In the WE BUILD context a \"legal entity\" is a company, business, sole trader, non-profit association or similar entity that is registered with a business registration authority or other public authority; most \"economic operators\" are therefore also \"legal entities\"."@en;
        skos:prefLabel                <urn:uuid:2eaee03b-3e77-4da9-8afd-2f29361a1080>;
        skos:related                  webuild:concept-109 , webuild:concept-94 , webuild:concept-6005 , webuild:concept-7 , webuild:concept-105;
        suomi-meta:creator            "4c00fd3e-ad5d-4ad6-8782-de29597a5d57";
        suomi-meta:modifier           "5dc030a4-740f-4dde-9548-4e6e797899d8";
        suomi-meta:publicationStatus  <http://uri.suomi.fi/codelist/interoperabilityplatform/interoperabilityplatform_status/code/DRAFT>;
        term:orderedBroader           ( webuild:concept-41 );
        term:orderedNarrower          ( webuild:concept-98 );
        term:orderedNote              ( "In the WE BUILD context a \"legal entity\" is a company, business, sole trader, non-profit association or similar entity that is registered with a business registration authority or other public authority; most \"economic operators\" are therefore also \"legal entities\"."@en "In WE BUILD, “legal entity” is intended as the transactional/legal identity used in B2B/B2G processes. It can include: a legal person (e.g., company), and in jurisdictions where applicable, a natural person acting as a registered business actor (e.g., sole trader) whose business identity is legally recognised and identifiable."@en );
        term:orderedRelated           ( webuild:concept-6005 webuild:concept-109 webuild:concept-94 webuild:concept-105 webuild:concept-7 ) .

<urn:uuid:e734dc6d-3e88-41e8-8b77-620971460acc>
        rdf:type                      skos-xl:Label;
